{"about_the_game":"Play as a shark or a diver in a dark aquatic world and overcome your enemies by employing cunning, teamwork, and stealth. Depth blends tension and visceral action as you team up against AI or be matched with other players in heart pounding combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play as a shark</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/274940/extras/PlayAsAShark.gif?t=1726299853\" /><br>As any one of <strong>7</strong> shark species, speed and senses are your greatest weapons. Stalk your prey from across the ocean and tear them in half with your razor sharp teeth. Be a Great White, Tiger, Mako, Bull , Hammerhead, Thresher ...... or even the legendary Megalodon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play as a diver</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/274940/extras/PlayAsADiver.gif?t=1726299853\" /><br>As a human diver you must explore the abyss in search of treasure to upgrade your arsenal. Defend yourself with a range of high powered gear, from spearguns and pistols to underwater assault rifles and explosive sea mines.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Heart pounding atmosphere</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/274940/extras/Atmosphere.gif?t=1726299853\" /><br>Experience the dread that comes from swimming in the darkness of the ocean. Dynamic lighting and shadows create a unique and gut-wrenching atmosphere that will have you on edge from the moment you dive in.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Evolve your play style</h2>Unlock exotic new weapons for your diver, or 'evolutions' for your shark that open up new tactical possibilities as you play the game. Persistent stat tracking and meaningful steam achievements will also give you something to shoot for (in some cases, quite literally!)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Practice offline with AI bots</h2>Not feeling quite ready to plunge into online play? Depth allows you to hone your skills against some alarmingly clever AI enemies who can be configured in several modes of difficulty.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gold Hoarder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/e6c1a49df968febb905562569b4c765bae78fc0f.jpg"},{"name":"Demo King","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/53fd1b046bf14f7f2fcd0f57745138873e46a4bf.jpg"},{"name":"All Leaderboards","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/00e95920be63e45349cea91ca11de166b1180b8b.jpg"},{"name":"Immortal Shark","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/91ac903ca9ce9dd381d2a00f258c7f526ca0fd33.jpg"},{"name":"All Or Nothing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/24adfcb478227655125dcd73fa4fdc5c78b8f5e7.jpg"},{"name":"Two Sharks One Spear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/edbfc792427c27f1a703a695e141a8cc39708d86.jpg"},{"name":"Sleeping With The Fishes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/8a3287339f240e85a3169aaf16ee44a8dbedbdae.jpg"},{"name":"Sneaky Diver","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/1ae39ce905c964a6a6cd2204f95817e55b501ee2.jpg"},{"name":"Expanding Horizons","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/c8246a8a563ab9e386ba53547f087c1e5b7bc502.jpg"},{"name":"Best Friends Forever","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/274940/f038d04eba4e8c981e6d2578fb25750403244989.jpg"}],"total":40},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/274940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726299853","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/274940/page.bg.jpg?t=1726299853","capsule_image":"https://shar